      <description>&lt;p&gt;Josiah is a skilled IT Professional from the Baltimore/Washington DC Area who specializes in DevOps, incident response, and workflow analysis. His work experience has given him a love of problem solving and engaging with unique situations. He has a strong background in open-source, and enjoys working in fast-paced environments with rapidly changing needs. In his day job, Josiah is a member of &lt;a href=&#34;https://adaptavist.com&#34;&gt;Adaptavist&amp;rsquo;s&lt;/a&gt; North American DevOps consulting team, where he spends his days helping clients revamp their development practices and build robust automation to support their strategies.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
